ygData.msgSnippet: Hmm no one walks up and gives me anything :( Hrmm... it can depends somewhat on servers. The older servers have more people giving stuff away. I hate
ygData.messageBody:
"Hmm no one walks up and gives me anything :(
"<br><br>Hrmm... it can depends somewhat on servers. The older
servers have more people giving stuff away. I hate to say
it... but the High End game on Drinal is
ridiculous.<br><br>I started November of 2000 and I still don't have a
high end character-- so I can't be 100%
sure.<br><br>But I've been told that about 40% of Drinal is 50+ or
has a character 50+. From what I can tell from the
consensus of people-- that's probably close to
truth.<br><br>So maybe that's why this server gives women more
items. LOL. Don't feel too bad. Course also you might be
playing a Troll, Iskar or Ogre female. It's kinda hard
sometimes to tell that they're female when people are
giving things away. <br><br>shooman out<br>Fatedhue
Prismatic<br><br>PS... this is not to say that I know the mentality for
certain of those that give away items to women that ask
for them or just stand there looking lost.
=)<br><br>I give away stuff to all just being myself. heh.
(when I do of course)<br><br>shoomie out
